Record Class Game_Record

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
dataAccess.Game_Record
Record Components:
gameID - unique gameID of the game being played
whiteUser - unique username of the player that is playing white
blackUser - unique username of the player that is playing black
gameName - name of the game being played
game - object of the game that is being played
